Peru’s Construction Activity ‘Reactivating,’ Velarde Says

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-09-16T17:16:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/peru-s-construction-activity-reactivating-velarde-says.html
Peru’s construction industry is
“reactivating,” even as economic growth begins to slow,
central bank President Julio Velarde said at a presentation in
 Lima  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
